<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application>xine User Interface</application></title>

<para>The <application>xine User Interface</application> package contains a user interface 
for <command>xine</command>. This is
useful for controlling the operations of your movie.</para>

<sect3><title>Package information</title>
<itemizedlist spacing='compact'>
<listitem><para>Download (HTTP): <ulink
url="&xine-ui-download-http;"/></para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Download (FTP): <ulink
url="&xine-ui-download-ftp;"/></para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Download size: &xine-ui-size;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Estimated Disk space required:
&xine-ui-buildsize;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Estimated build time:
&xine-ui-time;</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</sect3>

<sect3><title>Additional downloads</title>
<itemizedlist spacing='compact'>
<listitem><para>Required patch (if utilizing cURL): <ulink
url="&patch-root;/xine-ui-&xine-ui-version;-curl.patch"/>
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist></sect3>

<sect3><title><application>xine User Interface</application> dependencies</title>
<sect4><title>Required</title>
<para><xref linkend="xine-lib"/></para></sect4>
